{"title": "international patients", "author": null, "url": "https://www.uniklinik-duesseldorf.de/patienten-besucher/klinikeninstitutezentren/klinik-fuer-hals-nasen-ohrenheilkunde-hno/patienteninformationen/international-patients", "hostname": "uniklinik-duesseldorf.de", "description": null, "sitename": "UKD", "date": "2023-01-01", "id": null, "license": null, "body": null, "comments": "", "commentsbody": null, "raw_text": null, "text": "International Patients\nThe ear, nose and throat department of D\u00fcsseldorf University Hospital provides a full spectrum of medical and surgical solutions for disorders of the head and neck, or more restrictively called diseases of the ear, nose and throat \u2013 supported by cutting-edge precision diagnostic techniques.\nThe clinic hosts internationally renowned experienced ENT specialists, who lead the way in Germany, offering diversified treatment options for both pediatric and adult patients. The major sub-specialties of ENT Department of D\u00fcsseldorf University Hospital are:\n[Skull base surgery](https://www.uniklinik-duesseldorf.de/patienten-besucher/klinikeninstitutezentren/schaedelbasiszentrum)(benign or cancerous growths located on the underside of the brain, the base of the skull) [Otology and Audiology](/patienten-besucher/klinikeninstitutezentren/klinik-fuer-hals-nasen-ohrenheilkunde-hno/leistungsspektrum/ohr-otologie)(diseases of the ear, impaired hearing, balance problems, cochlea implant, semi-implantable hearing aids)\n- Laryngology (voice and swallowing affection)\n[Head and neck surgery](/patienten-besucher/klinikeninstitutezentren/klinik-fuer-hals-nasen-ohrenheilkunde-hno/klinik/kopf-hals-tumorzentrum)(surgical treatment of head and neck cancers, abnormalities of the thyroid, lymphatic glands) [Plastic and reconstructive surgeries](/patienten-besucher/klinikeninstitutezentren/klinik-fuer-hals-nasen-ohrenheilkunde-hno/leistungsspektrum/plastische-und-rekonstruktive-chirurgie)of the face (functional and aesthetic treatments, Botox therapy) [Pediatric ENT disorders](/patienten-besucher/klinikeninstitutezentren/klinik-fuer-hals-nasen-ohrenheilkunde-hno/leistungsspektrum/kinder)(adenoids, ear effussion, tracheal abnormalities)\n- Facial nerve disorders\n[Salivary gland disorders](/patienten-besucher/klinikeninstitutezentren/klinik-fuer-hals-nasen-ohrenheilkunde-hno/leistungsspektrum/speicheldruesen)(conservative treatment, sialendoscopy, surgical treatment of glands) [Surgical sleep medicine](/patienten-besucher/klinikeninstitutezentren/klinik-fuer-hals-nasen-ohrenheilkunde-hno/leistungsspektrum/schlafmedizin)(sleep apnea therapy, snoring therapy) [Appointment](#)\nPlease make an appointment in advance by email (sekretariat-hno@med.uni-duesseldorf.de) or telephone (+49) 211-81 17571.\n[Medical records](#)\nPlease bring all your medical records from previous physicians to your scheduled appointment.\n[Translator](#)\nWe offer patient care in German and English language. If you speak another language we would kindly ask you to organize a translator for consultation.\n[Treatment costs](#)\nPayment can be easily done after outpatient visit cash or with credit card.", "language": null, "image": null, "pagetype": null, "links": ["/", "https://www.uni-duesseldorf.de", "#", "#", "#", "#", "tel:112", "tel:+492118117012", "/ueber-das-ukd/lageplan-anfahrt", "/patienten-besucher/notfall", "/ueber-das-ukd/presse-publikationen", "/ueber-das-ukd/kontakt", "#", "#", "/patienten-besucher", "/patienten-besucher/kliniken/institute/zentren", "/patienten-besucher/als-patient-am-ukd", "/patienten-besucher/beratung-und-unterstuetzung", "/patienten-besucher/veranstaltungen", "/patienten-besucher/notfall", "/forschung-lehre", "http://www.medizin.hhu.de/", "/patienten-besucher/kliniken/institute/zentren", "http://www.medizin.hhu.de/forschung.html", "/forschung-lehre/coronavirus-forschung", "http://www.medizin.hhu.de/studium-und-lehre.html", "/forschung-lehre/startup4med", "https://www.graduiertenzent